review_blob: One of my favourite APA from Russian craft brewery. Aroma is very citrus, flavour, taste is very complex with taste of great American hops, aftertaste is very rich and very long. Great brew!
The best czech pilsner that i ever had. Aroma hop and taste is fantastic, bitter and dry taste. Svijany, keep it going! : )

One of the best bock beer in Russia. Alcohol is not feelin when i served this in glass for belgian beer, aroma is flavoured with white bread, some alcohol notes, taste is creamy, fruity, little honey and little touch of hop, after sip i feelin aftertaste like ale :) Its a very decent Russian bock, recommended!
Very poor taste for weissbier, dissapointed me. But many woman like this beer for light taste, i prefer more complex wiessbier like legendary Weihenstephaner or Andechs. Dont want to buy it again!
This is real masterpiece, fantastic brew from legendary America Brewery! Paradise aroma, awesome burned-friut aftertaste. Worldclass, 100/100 ! Real must have for beerhunters!

One of my favourite Baltic porter beer and truly one of the best beers from Russia! Fantastic vine taste with burnt aftertaste, very complex and rich beer, best serve at indoor temperature, usually i drink 0,5 l of this beer about one hour : ) Real beer for meditation, strongly recommended!
